<atten4>
<ptxt>Tape the screwdriver tip before use.</ptxt>
</atten4>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Remove the dust cover set ring and dust cover from the lower arm.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Using SST, remove the ball joint.</ptxt>
